WritePackedQuaternion in Serializer.h always returns false, because the bytes written are not checked against the size of the coords array but the size of the quaternion against.
Just change line 134 in Serializer.cpp from:

return Write(&coords[0], sizeof coords) == sizeof value;

to:

return Write(&coords[0], sizeof coords) == sizeof coords;
